thread.title: BRIEF-ExpreS2ion Rights Issue Oversubscribed

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-ExpreS2ion Rights Issue Oversubscribed
text:
March 2 (Reuters) - EXPRES2ION BIOTECH HOLDING AB :
* PRESS RELEASE - EXPRES2ION’S RIGHTS ISSUE OVERSUBSCRIBED
* ‍RIGHTS ISSUE OF APPROXIMATELY SEK 19.2 MILLION HAS BEEN OVERSUBSCRIBED​
* ‍RIGHTS ISSUE WAS SUBSCRIBED TO APPROXIMATELY SEK 30.3 MILLION
* ‍RIGHTS ISSUE WAS SUBSCRIBED TO APPROXIMATELY SEK 30.3 MILLION, CORRESPONDING TO A SUBSCRIPTION RATE OF APPROXIMATELY 158 PERCENT​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
